Follow these steps to redeem your unique Bluemix promo code. Remember that your promo code can be used only once; please do not share it.

(1) Register for an IBM Bluemix trial account: ibm.biz/bluemixsv
		You will be asked to validate your email address, so please check your inbox and click the validation link.
   
(2) Log in to your IBM Bluemix dashboard, click the number of days remaining on your account in the upper right corner, and click promo code.

(3) Type your promo code into the “Enter promo code” field, and click APPLY.

(4) Refresh the page to see the extension reflected in the calendar icon.
